        Two officers of each class are needed. Once an officer, always an officer unless for some reason you're abusing the status in some way. <br> <br>Primary resonsibilites will be to interview prospective members, arrange events and otherwise promote and maintain the guild.  <br> <br>Membership should be restricted to those that actually want to be in this guild (as opposed to any guild), speak in normal words (not chat-speak), and are gnomes. <br> <br>Things have been slow these past couple weeks with Belwar having to leave so suddenly, but I hope to change this. This guild has a lot of potential and needs energetic officers to help tap that potential! So if you are interrested, email me directly or post here.

